| [layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/layout.tsx) | 38 | Wraps all four modes | Provides `PracticeProvider` context + renders `DrawerOverlay`. Persists across mode navigations so context isn't lost. |
| [template.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/template.tsx) | 59 | Auth guard + transition | Re-mounts children on every navigation. Checks auth via `useEffect` → redirects to `/lab?mode=login` if not authenticated. Wraps children in a framer-motion 150ms fade-in. |
| [PracticeContext.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/context/PracticeContext.tsx) | 86 | Shared state provider | Holds: (1) the static `SHEET` data, (2) a `Map<string, DSAProblem>` index for O(1) lookups, (3) the floating drawer state (which problem is open, click position for animation origin). That's it — no user state, no API data, no attempt data. |
| [DrawerOverlay.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/components/DrawerOverlay.tsx) | 38 | Drawer mount point | Reads `activeDrawer` from context, resolves the problem via `problemIndex.get()`, and renders `ProblemDrawer` with `AnimatePresence` for enter/exit animations. Lives at layout level so the drawer can be opened from any mode. |
| [PracticeHeader.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/components/PracticeHeader.tsx) | 94 | Mode navigation bar | Fixed 48px header with 4 mode pills (Browse/Focus/Analyze/Interview). Uses `layoutId="activePracticeMode"` for a shared spring-animated underline. Has a `{children}` right slot where each mode passes its own controls (timer, time range picker, etc.). |

