| [sheet.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/data/sheet.ts) | 3,007 | Problem catalog | A **124KB** TypeScript file exporting `SHEET: DSATopic[]` — an array of topics each containing an array of `DSAProblem` objects. Each problem has: `id`, `title`, `url`, `platform`, `tags[]` (mixing difficulty + algorithm + meta labels), `description`. Also has an unused `isCompleted?: boolean` field. Contains 450+ problems across ~20 topics. |

