| File | Lines | Purpose | What It Actually Does |
|------|-------|---------|----------------------|
| [useProblemFilters.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/hooks/useProblemFilters.ts) | 157 | Filtering/sorting engine | Takes `savedProblems`, `completedProblems`, and `extensionMap` (attempt summaries from browser extension). Provides 5 filter dimensions: search text, status (All/Saved/Completed/Unresolved/Due for Review/Never Attempted), difficulty (Easy/Medium/Hard), platform (LeetCode/GFG/Other), and sort (Difficulty/Staleness/Attempts with asc/desc). Returns the filtered `SHEET` copy. All filter state is `useState` — **nothing persists across navigation or to URL**. |
