| [useScrollSync.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/xandar-lab/app/lab/practice/hooks/useScrollSync.ts) | 37 | Scroll-spy for topic sidebar | Uses `IntersectionObserver` on `[data-topic]` elements inside `#problem-scroll-container` with 0.4 threshold. Returns `activeTopic` string. Only consumed by `TopicSidebar`. |

