## Part 3: API Endpoints Used

| Endpoint | Method | Used By | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|---------|
| `/api/attempts/summary` | GET | BrowseView | Per-problem solve time, submissions, stuck, review-due |
| `/api/analytics/activity` | GET | BrowseView | Weekly solve delta |
| `/api/analytics?range=` | GET | AnalyzeDashboard | Full performance analytics |
| `/api/suggestions` | GET | TodaysFocus, FocusEmpty | Personalized problem suggestions |
| `/api/problems/save` | POST | BrowseView | Toggle save/unsave problem |
| `/api/problems/complete` | POST | BrowseView | Toggle complete/incomplete problem |
| `/api/attempts` | GET/POST/PUT/DELETE | ProblemDrawer, FocusCard, InterviewReport | Full CRUD for problem attempts |
| `/api/attempts/discussions` | GET/POST | ProblemDrawer | Discussion threads on attempts |
| `/api/explanations` | GET/POST | ProblemDrawer | "Explain" feature + AI feedback |
| `/api/interviews` | GET/POST | InterviewManager | List/create interview sessions |
| `/api/interviews/{id}` | GET/PUT | ActiveInterview, InterviewReport | Get session / end session |
| `/api/interviews/{id}/message` | POST | ActiveInterview | Send message during interview |

